page.title: 17Birds seen in the area
page.content: Blackbird, Collard Dove, Crow, Curlew, Dipper, Fieldfare, Finches (Bullfinch, Chaffinch, Greenfinch), Hawks (Kestrel, Sparrow), House Martins, Jackdaw, Lapwing, Linnet, Magpie, Meadow Pipit, Owls (Tawny, Barn), Reed Bunting, Robin, Skylark, Song Thrush, Sparrows (Hedge, House, Tree), Starling, Swallow, Swan (Mute), Swift, Tits (Blue, Great), Wagtails (Grey, Pied, Yellow), Warblers (Garden, Wood), Water Fowl (Coot, Mallard, Moorhen, Pochard, Ruddy Duck, Tufted Duck), Wren, Yellow Hammer.
